OL,3,CLifer's bid to move to open prison
OL,4,Cdelayed
OL,6,FA convicted killer's controversial bid
OL,7,Fto be moved to an open prison has been
OL,8,Fdelayed after his parole hearing was
OL,9,Fdeferred.
OL,11,FMartin Bell was given a life sentence
OL,12,F- with a minimum term of 12 years - in
OL,13,FDecember 2014 for the manslaughter of
OL,14,FLeeds woman Gemma Simpson.
OL,16,FMiss Simpson was 23 when taxi driver
OL,17,FBell attacked her with a knife and a
OL,18,Fhammer at his flat in Harrogate in
OL,19,F2000.
