OL,6,FHe then dismembered her body and
OL,7,Fburied it at Brimham Rocks in North
OL,8,FYorkshire, where it lay undiscovered
OL,9,Funtil he handed himself in to police
OL,10,Fin 2014.
OL,12,FHe later pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fmanslaughter on the grounds of
OL,14,Fdiminished responsibility after being
OL,15,Fdiagnosed with schizophrenia.
