OL,3,CLifer's bid to move to open prison
OL,4,Cdelayed
OL,6,FA parole hearing was due to be held on
OL,7,FTuesday to decide whether Bell, now
OL,8,F55, could be transferred to a category
OL,9,FD open prison, where inmates face
OL,10,Fminimal security and can leave the
OL,11,Fprison for work and education.
OL,13,FMiss Simpson's family said the
OL,14,Fprospect of Bell being granted greater
OL,15,Ffreedoms was "frightening".
OL,17,FThe Parole Board has now confirmed
OL,18,FBell's hearing has been delayed, but
OL,19,Fhas not revealed why.
