OL,3,CLifer's bid to move to open prison
OL,4,Cdelayed
OL,6,FA spokesman said: "The Parole Board
OL,7,Fcannot comment on individual cases. A
OL,8,Fpanel may adjourn a parole hearing to
OL,9,Fensure a comprehensive risk assessment
OL,10,Fcan take place.
OL,12,F"There are a number of situations
OL,13,Fwhere an adjournment may be required,
OL,14,Ffor example more information is
OL,15,Frequired, the prisoner needs more time
OL,16,Fto complete a course, a witness is not
OL,17,Favailable, or for some other
OL,18,Funavoidable reason. The Parole Board
OL,19,Fdoes everything it can to avoid these
OL,20,Fdelays."
